<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM2.9">
<l>muṟṟat tūṭu pukuntu niṉmukaṅ kāṭṭip puṉmuṟu valceytu</l>
<l>ciṟṟilō ṭeṅkaḷ cintai yumcitaik kakkaṭa vaiyō kōvintā</l>
<l>muṟṟa maṇṇiṭan tāvi viṇṇuṟa nīṇṭaḷantu koṇṭā yemmaip</l>
<l>paṟṟi meyppiṇak kiṭṭak kālintap pakkam niṉṟavareṉ collār</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Entering the middle of the courtyard, showing [us] Your face, and smiling gently,</l>
<l>Do you have to destroy our thoughts along with the little [sand] houses, O Govinda?</l>
<l>O You who measured the sky growing [so high] as to touch [it],</l>
<l rend="indent">Having taken the [vast] space of the earth by pacing [it with another leg]!</l>
<l>growing so that the sky is touched [and by] measuring [it]!!</l>
<l>If You grasp [us] and embrace our bodies, what will these bystanders not say?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
